<sect1 id="dir_014d03f1fa745a752e3155249a7cef2e_1autotoc_md196">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::gamestate</title><para>Game state management for the helios engine.</para>
<para>This module provides domain-specific types and bindings for managing game states (Title, Running, Paused). It uses the generic <computeroutput><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1state" kindref="compound">helios::engine::state</ref></computeroutput> framework.</para>
</sect1>
