<sect1 id="dir_014d03f1fa745a752e3155249a7cef2e_1autotoc_md199">
<title>Architecture</title><para><computeroutput>GameStateManager</computeroutput> is a type alias for <computeroutput>StateManager&lt;GameState&gt;</computeroutput>:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">using<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1gamestate_1a8cbc47f1a88e13102691fea025f40461" kindref="member">GameStateManager</ref><sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1state_1_1StateManager" kindref="compound">helios::engine::state::StateManager&lt;types::GameState&gt;</ref>;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>The generic <computeroutput>StateManager</computeroutput> provides:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Rule-based transitions with optional guards</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Listener notifications on state changes</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Command-driven state changes via <computeroutput>StateCommand&lt;GameState&gt;</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
